Earthquake-prone Turkey is currently considering a bid on a nuclear power
plant tender from a Japanese energy company. [Selene Verri from _Turkish
Diary_ asks](http://turkishdiary.blogspot.com/2011/03/turkey-going-nuclear-is-
it-wise-after.html): “So, Turkey is going nuclear. Is it wise, knowing what
just happened in Japan, a conscientious and prepared country?”

